| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5325 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f7fb0af0-9c09-509d-9cae-9346ef14bfa6"
